{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Chertovica</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>SLASH, PUNCH, and SHOOT </strong>your way through spawns of hell, monsters and demons. Face off against brutal hordes of cherts, vampires, navs and other vermin coming straights from hell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320270/extras/Combat.gif?t=1736508479\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Darkness has fallen upon the world. Experience the <strong>thick atmosphere of a demon invasion</strong>, but are the horrors coming from hell, or are you, the horror, coming to hell?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320270/extras/Divozienka.gif?t=1736508479\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Revel in the nostalgia of retro games with a modern twist! </strong>Chertovica brings back the gritty charm of pixelated textures, 2.5D worlds and 8 bit sounds to bring each battle scene to life. Experience the excitement of retro visuals paired with the smoothness and clarity of today\u2019s gaming.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320270/extras/Portal.gif?t=1736508479\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>And when the dust settles, grab yourself a well-earned cold one!</strong> Because after a battle well-fought, every warrior deserves to sit back, relax, and savor their hard-won victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320270/extras/Hedgefence.gif?t=1736508479\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320270/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736508479","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320270/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736508479","ca